<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥ -<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص١٤٦:</span> قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى: {وَأَصْحَابُ الشِّمَالِ مَا أَصْحَابُ الشِّمَالِ <span class="c2">(٤١)</span> فِي سَمُومٍ وَحَمِيمٍ <span class="c2">(٤٢)</span> وَظِلٍّ مِنْ يَحْمُومٍ <span class="c2">(٤٣)</span> لَا بَارِدٍ وَلَا كَرِيمٍ <span class="c2">(٤٤)</span> إِنَّهُمْ كَانُوا قَبْلَ ذَلِكَ مُتْرَفِينَ <span class="c2">(٤٥)</span> وَكَانُوا يُصِرُّونَ عَلَى الْحِنْثِ الْعَظِيمِ <span class="c2">(٤٦)</span>} <span class="c4">[الواقعة: ٤١ - ٤٦]</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ مُجَاهِدٌ:</span> <span class="c3">{يَحْمُومٍ}</span>: <span class="c2">«دُخَانٌ أَسْوَدُ»</span>،<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c3">{مُتْرَفِينَ}</span>: <span class="c2">«مُمَتَّعِينَ»</span>،<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ مُجَاهِدٌ:</span> <span class="c3">{يُصِرُّونَ}</span>: <span class="c2">«يُدِيمُونَ»</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>